sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Application
    participant Database
    participant EncryptionService

    User->>Application: Send data
    Application->>EncryptionService: Encrypt data in transit
    EncryptionService-->>Application: Return encrypted data
    Application->>Database: Store encrypted data
    Database-->>Application: Acknowledge storage
    Application->>User: Confirm data stored securely

    User->>Application: Request data
    Application->>Database: Retrieve encrypted data
    Database-->>Application: Return encrypted data
    Application->>EncryptionService: Decrypt data at rest
    EncryptionService-->>Application: Return decrypted data
    Application->>User: Send decrypted data